The Palestinian militant group Islamic Jihad says it has ordered its gunmen in
the Gaza Strip to stop firing rockets at Israeli targets while Israel prepares
for and completes its Gaza evacuation.
The group issued a statement Wednesday, a day after errant rocket fire into
